downloadTitle: FSOCS performance analysis and capacity planning document
downloadDescription: Document provides insights into performance testing and analysis conducted for the Forefront security for Office Communication Server
detailsSection: Document provides insights into performance testing and analysis conducted for the Forefront security for Office Communication Server. The document also provides the user with the information needed to petform capacity planning for the deployment and installation of Forefront Security for Office Communication Server.
installInstructionSection:
Click Download, and then click Save.
Browse to the location you want to save the file to, and then click Save.
Browse to the location where you saved the file.
Double-click the file to open it.
